WEBVTT

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:05.760
(Previously)
I've got a new target.

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.560
P'Fah?!

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:08.880
Teh.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:12.480
Jimmy, my brother, Toh.

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.960
Don't fall for Jimmy.

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:19.360
Jimmy is a certified player.

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:21.480
I don't want you getting hurt.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:22.840
Come on!

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.040
I wasn't thinking of anything.

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:27.280
I don't want my brother to fall for you.

00:00:27.633 --> 00:00:29.193
I haven't thought of him that way at all.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:55.000
You bastard, Jimmy!

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.920
What's your problem, Teh?

00:00:58.160 --> 00:00:59.000
Look at this.

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:02.120
What the hell is this?!

00:01:10.360 --> 00:01:12.840
It's obviously your house's camera.

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:18.440
Don't forget that I'm your
friend who knows you really are.

00:01:18.440 --> 00:01:19.200
So what?
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:19.880 --> 00:01:24.000
I just bought desserts to
thank your brother for dinner.

00:01:25.240 --> 00:01:28.480
Didn't I tell you to stay away from my brother?!

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:32.720
- I don't trust you!
- So what?!

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:34.200
- Didn't I tell you?!
- What the hell?!

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:35.800
What's your game?!

00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:36.880
I don't have a plan!

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:38.600
- Calm down, man!
- Spit it out!

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:39.840
- Just tell me, damn it!
- Take it easy!

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:40.840
Calm down!

00:01:41.440 --> 00:01:42.080
Calm down!

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:43.440
What's wrong with you?

00:01:46.120 --> 00:01:49.240
Both of you are too worked up. Let's talk later.

00:01:49.720 --> 00:01:50.160
Move it.

00:01:50.160 --> 00:01:52.160
- Come at me!
- Stop!

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:52.800
Come at me!

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:55.720
- Enough.
- Let me go!

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:05.200
Run, let go.

00:02:08.040 --> 00:02:10.600
If you don't even like Teh's brother,
then why do all this?

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:12.840
What?

00:02:13.640 --> 00:02:14.160
You jealous?

00:02:15.880 --> 00:02:16.640
Please.

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:18.240
I've already moved on.

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:21.440
It's Book, a model.

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:24.200
That was fast.

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:26.160
Look who you're talking to.

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:32.960
I dragged you here to
talk some sense into you.

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:40.320
Teh's your best friend. Think about
things before you do something stupid.

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.880
I understand that you'd…

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:44.160
screw anything that moves.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:47.040
But he's your friend's brother.

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:49.320
Leave him out of this.

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:54.240
Oh,

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.200
I heard that you're…

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:59.400
hitting on P'Fah?

00:03:02.160 --> 00:03:02.880
How'd you know?

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:05.040
Ah…

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:07.520
Good luck with that.

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:10.800
He's way out of your league.

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:16.640
Yeah! Just watch me!

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:18.040
I'll make him mine.

00:03:44.600 --> 00:03:47.120
Or didn't Jimmy think of P'Toh that way?

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:54.560
Forget it.

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:56.200
It already happened.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:16.000
"Love Alert"
(Episode 2)

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:28.080
Teh is being such a pain about his brother.

00:05:38.920 --> 00:05:41.360
How can I get close to Plaifah?

00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:56.640
Maybe I can use P'Toh to get to him.

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:04.200
Yeah, P'Toh.

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:06.600
He's my best bet.

00:06:12.680 --> 00:06:15.320
But how do I handle him?

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:30.440
This looks amazing, Jimmy.

00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:32.760
It sure does.

00:06:37.760 --> 00:06:40.720
You say it looks good,
but you're not looking at the food.

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:44.600
Did I ever say I was talking about the food?

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:54.960
P' Toh,

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:58.200
could you spill some
of the drink on your lips?

00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:03.040
So I can wipe it off for you.

00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:07.160
Just like this.

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:20.160
P' Toh,

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.480
there's something I must tell you.

00:07:29.080 --> 00:07:30.320
It's important.

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:38.040
What… is it?

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:46.640
Teh's in love with P'Fah.

00:07:51.080 --> 00:07:52.400
I don't know what to do about it.

00:07:54.880 --> 00:07:56.720
R-really?

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:57.920
Yes.

00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:03.120
Can you do me a favor?

00:08:06.320 --> 00:08:09.280
Yes. What do you need me to do?

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:24.760
What's with the sudden party?
Aren't you supposed to be an “inverter”?

00:08:24.760 --> 00:08:26.600
It's “introvert”.

00:08:27.200 --> 00:08:28.720
An “inverter” is a part of an AC.

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:32.000
Fine, my bad. Excuse me.

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:35.920
What's the reason?

00:08:36.920 --> 00:08:38.160
Nothing much.

00:08:38.920 --> 00:08:43.120
I just want to cook for some
friends before the cafe opens.

00:08:47.160 --> 00:08:47.840
Sure?

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:50.680
Are you a detective or something?

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:55.520
And who exactly are these “friends”?

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:59.640
Well, there's… Fah.

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:03.240
And that's it.

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:09.240
You have the nerve to call
that a party? That's a date.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:12.160
You're coming too, so it's not a date anymore.

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:17.400
Unless... you're not joining?

00:09:19.400 --> 00:09:23.720
No way! Half of the money
is mine. I need to eat my money's worth.

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:37.560
I'm heading out.

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:39.280
See ya.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.320
Okay.

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:43.640
Study hard.

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:08.640
Hey,

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:12.320
What's with the long faces?
What are you guys doing?

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:13.913
How can I not be stressed?

00:10:14.313 --> 00:10:17.033
I've been working on the group report
all night and it's still not finished.

00:10:17.800 --> 00:10:18.840
Which report?

00:10:20.760 --> 00:10:21.840
This one. For Professor Boss.

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:27.200
- Crap…
- I knew it.

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:30.480
- We're toast.
- We're screwed.

00:10:32.840 --> 00:10:35.320
What am I going to tell him?

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:40.120
Will he let me turn it in late?

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:46.360
What do I do?!

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:52.640
Mr. Teh?

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:55.880
Yes, professor?

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:59.440
Do you want to revise your report? I can't let
you make changes after it's been submitted.

00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:03.480
S… Submitted?

00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:07.120
Yes, Mr. Jimmy dropped it off this morning.

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:10.600
I've had a quick look at it.
You guys did a solid job.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:13.600
Yes.

00:11:56.640 --> 00:11:58.800
Why did you put my name on the report?

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:00.920
Weren't you still pissed at me?

00:12:01.520 --> 00:12:03.960
I don't take our problem personally.

00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:07.920
Stop overthinking it, dumbass.

00:12:09.160 --> 00:12:12.600
If I'm a dumbass, then you're a total moron.

00:12:16.040 --> 00:12:17.000
I totally get you…

00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:20.640
for being protective of your brother.

00:12:22.040 --> 00:12:24.840
I can't help it. He's so cute.

00:12:25.160 --> 00:12:26.640
Hey, watch it…

00:12:26.640 --> 00:12:27.520
Chill out.

00:12:29.560 --> 00:12:31.080
I'm just telling the truth.

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:38.640
You should know that
I'm worried about him.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:41.200
I don't want him to get hurt.

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:44.640
As long as you don't mess with him,

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:47.160
we're good.

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:52.760
Need anything else? I'm running late.

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:53.960
Nothing.

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:55.240
I'm off then.

00:12:56.920 --> 00:12:57.480
Wait!

00:12:58.120 --> 00:13:01.160
We're having a party at
my house. You should come.

00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:03.680
But no flirting with my brother.

00:13:05.880 --> 00:13:07.840
I got it. See ya there.

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:10.160
Whatever.

00:13:28.480 --> 00:13:29.680
Whoa!

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:31.760
Hi there, P'Toh!

00:13:32.200 --> 00:13:33.840
I can smell it from the street!

00:13:38.280 --> 00:13:39.760
Go wash your hands first.

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.200
Feed me then?

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:46.200
My hands are messy too.
Go wash yours and help yourself.

00:13:47.600 --> 00:13:48.320
Meanie.

00:13:49.880 --> 00:13:50.880
I won't eat then.

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:53.880
Gonna take a shower first.

00:13:59.720 --> 00:14:00.800
Everything looks amazing.

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:03.560
I'm so jealous of Teh.

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:05.880
Oh, P'Toh,

00:14:07.080 --> 00:14:07.840
I bought some drinks.

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:09.560
Thanks.

00:14:10.840 --> 00:14:14.440
You said the food looks good,
make sure you eat a lot.

00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:15.800
Of course.

00:14:21.120 --> 00:14:22.080
I'll check it for you.

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:36.920
You're here for P'Toh?
You've got the right house.

00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:40.160
I thought so.
I was sure I remembered the way.

00:14:42.640 --> 00:14:44.760
So… is P'Toh inside?

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:45.840
Yep.

00:14:57.640 --> 00:14:58.320
P'Toh.

00:14:59.160 --> 00:14:59.760
Fah.

00:15:00.680 --> 00:15:02.840
I told you not to bring anything.

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:05.392
I heard we're having roasted beef.

00:15:05.465 --> 00:15:08.432
It goes well with
this wine. I even “borrowed” it from my parents.

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:11.120
That sounds like a killer combo.

00:15:13.920 --> 00:15:15.000
Do you need any help?

00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:19.120
Not at all. Wait for Teh to finish
his shower, then we can dig in.

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:22.280
Are you hungry?
I can go and hurry him up.

00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:23.680
No need to rush him.

00:15:25.120 --> 00:15:28.280
P'Toh, where's the toilet?
I want to use it.

00:15:29.400 --> 00:15:30.560
It's near the kitchen.

00:15:40.920 --> 00:15:42.200
Need my help?

00:15:43.600 --> 00:15:46.600
Don't worry. Have a seat.
I'll take care of the rest.

00:15:57.640 --> 00:15:58.520
P'Fah?

00:15:59.360 --> 00:16:00.000
Hello.

00:16:02.720 --> 00:16:04.880
Let's eat! I'm starving!

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:05.600
“P”?

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:09.200
So we're still at “P”?

00:16:10.400 --> 00:16:11.280
Challenge accepted.

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:26.160
Yeah, you had a fever at the volunteer camp.

00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:31.680
I still remember. If I hadn't sponged you down,
you wouldn't have made it off the mountains.

00:16:32.600 --> 00:16:33.080
Yeah.

00:16:33.880 --> 00:16:35.160
That camp was so much fun.

00:16:37.520 --> 00:16:39.040
I'm going to wash my hands.

00:16:45.040 --> 00:16:46.160
Do you like the beach?

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:50.200
Not really, I'm more of a mountain person.

00:16:51.800 --> 00:16:55.600
P'Toh, let's go on a trip soon.
I'm craving a chill barbecue night.

00:16:56.760 --> 00:16:58.840
Sure. Just name the date.

00:16:59.480 --> 00:17:00.200
You said it.

00:17:00.880 --> 00:17:02.080
I'll clear my schedule.

00:17:08.360 --> 00:17:09.600
(Ask him.)

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:15.120
Is it “date” schedule for a boyfriend?

00:17:16.800 --> 00:17:17.920
Study schedule.

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:23.200
Since my last breakup, I haven't been looking
for anything serious. Just one-night stands.

00:17:31.360 --> 00:17:33.240
(Ask him more.)

00:17:34.640 --> 00:17:39.120
So, is it true that you're seeing a girl now?

00:17:40.520 --> 00:17:41.320
Yeah.

00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:44.440
It's more comfortable than being with men.

00:17:45.440 --> 00:17:48.360
Because all I ever met were players.

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:53.480
They act sweet to your face, then go screw
someone else behind your back. I hate that.

00:17:55.560 --> 00:17:59.040
If you ever date someone,
I have to screen them first.

00:18:00.760 --> 00:18:01.520
Okay?

00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:06.240
Okay.

00:18:16.760 --> 00:18:17.600
Are you full?

00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:19.200
Yes. What about you?

00:18:41.840 --> 00:18:43.160
Thanks for tonight.

00:18:46.440 --> 00:18:51.760
Say bye to Teh for me. He knocked out
right after dinner and hasn't moved since.

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:53.840
Want me to wake him up?

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:54.840
It's fine.

00:18:55.440 --> 00:18:56.840
I'll head out now.

00:18:57.960 --> 00:18:59.040
Go home safe.

00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:01.360
See ya, P'Toh.

00:19:01.720 --> 00:19:02.160
See ya.

00:19:15.280 --> 00:19:16.080
P'Fah?

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:17.560
Hello.

00:19:20.280 --> 00:19:22.440
Let's eat! I'm starving!

00:19:22.440 --> 00:19:23.200
“P”?

00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:33.640
This is going to be fun.

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:47.080
That's the last of them.

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:51.840
Thanks. Go hang out with Teh.
I've got the rest.

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:53.560
No way.

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:56.240
We ate together, we clean together.

00:19:58.920 --> 00:20:02.480
No. In this house, we don't
let our guests do the dishes.

00:20:04.560 --> 00:20:05.720
P'Toh.

00:20:06.360 --> 00:20:10.640
In my house, we don't sit around
while the host cleans up.

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:12.320
It's okay.

00:20:12.320 --> 00:20:12.960
P'Toh.

00:20:13.560 --> 00:20:14.480
It's fine.

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:15.280
P'Toh.

00:20:15.720 --> 00:20:16.760
- Come on.
- I mean it.

00:20:17.520 --> 00:20:18.160
- No...
- P'Toh...

00:20:43.400 --> 00:20:45.040
P'Toh!

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:51.480
Why didn't you tell me to sleep upstairs?

00:20:52.120 --> 00:20:54.840
My whole body is stiff
from sleeping on a couch.

00:20:57.480 --> 00:20:58.480
Why are you still here?

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:01.600
I was helping P'Toh with the dishes.

00:21:02.360 --> 00:21:03.080
Good.

00:21:03.800 --> 00:21:05.480
You can be grateful.

00:21:06.120 --> 00:21:06.880
Finish the rest for us.

00:21:08.360 --> 00:21:10.360
You're leaving me to do it all by myself?!

00:21:10.360 --> 00:21:13.800
Duh, I took a shower and
don't want to get messy.

00:21:14.560 --> 00:21:16.320
And what about P'Toh?!

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:18.840
He must sing me a lullaby!

00:21:19.040 --> 00:21:20.480
Any questions, moron?

00:21:28.760 --> 00:21:30.320
Why is my heart racing?

00:21:34.240 --> 00:21:37.680
I like Fah, I like Fah…

00:21:38.280 --> 00:21:39.320
I like Fah.

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:46.960
You like Fah, Jimmy.

00:21:47.600 --> 00:21:48.360
You like Fah.

00:22:20.280 --> 00:22:23.240
Finally! We're here!

00:22:26.760 --> 00:22:27.240
Fah,

00:22:28.400 --> 00:22:31.520
Are you okay back there?
I tried to drive as smoothly as I could.

00:22:31.920 --> 00:22:33.520
I took some meds beforehand.

00:22:37.720 --> 00:22:38.800
Here, let me get that for you.

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:40.840
It's okay. I can manage.

00:22:47.760 --> 00:22:49.000
You carry the cooler.

00:22:49.360 --> 00:22:50.240
Fine…

00:23:02.720 --> 00:23:04.040
Fah's barely talking to me.

00:23:05.280 --> 00:23:07.320
You're being way too clingy.

00:23:07.560 --> 00:23:09.120
What am I supposed to do?

00:23:09.920 --> 00:23:13.160
Play it cool. Make him wonder about you.

00:23:13.846 --> 00:23:16.726
Like your advice ever works.

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:21.000
I'm being this “extra”,

00:23:21.920 --> 00:23:23.480
but he still ignores me.

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:29.680
If I “stay still”, I'd be…

00:23:31.560 --> 00:23:32.360
invisible.

00:23:33.680 --> 00:23:36.320
Whatever. That's all I can help.

00:23:37.520 --> 00:23:38.440
Sure…

00:23:39.400 --> 00:23:41.080
An advice from a single guy.

00:23:43.040 --> 00:23:45.920
I'm single not because my methods don't work,

00:23:46.440 --> 00:23:48.720
but by choice. Period.

00:24:28.280 --> 00:24:29.840
Is there a problem between us?

00:24:43.120 --> 00:24:43.800
Not at all.

00:24:44.880 --> 00:24:49.080
I saw you taking photos and
didn't want to get in your way.

00:24:52.280 --> 00:24:53.720
P-P'Fah?

00:24:54.800 --> 00:24:55.840
Did you take a picture of me?

00:24:56.920 --> 00:24:59.640
Yeah. Now, you're the subject.

00:25:00.680 --> 00:25:02.720
But I'm not photogenic.

00:25:03.320 --> 00:25:04.240
Come take a look.

00:25:24.360 --> 00:25:25.040
I think…

00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:29.000
I'm really into you.

00:25:34.560 --> 00:25:37.600
And next time, drop the “P”.

00:25:38.560 --> 00:25:39.400
Just call me Fah.

00:25:42.720 --> 00:25:43.640
Got it?

00:26:14.320 --> 00:26:15.120
Damn…

00:26:16.480 --> 00:26:17.800
My heart's fluttering.

00:26:49.720 --> 00:26:51.360
What are you up to?

00:26:52.560 --> 00:26:53.720
Marinating the pork.

00:26:54.280 --> 00:26:55.160
You startled me.

00:26:59.633 --> 00:27:01.793
What do I have to do? Need a hand?

00:27:02.640 --> 00:27:05.320
Put all the ingredients in and massage them.

00:27:51.960 --> 00:27:53.040
Your hands are so soft.

00:27:58.080 --> 00:28:01.640
Then… you finish the rest.

00:28:02.680 --> 00:28:06.360
I'm going to… wash the vegetables.

00:28:18.760 --> 00:28:20.320
Hold on, Jimmy.

00:28:21.480 --> 00:28:22.360
You like Fah.

00:28:48.440 --> 00:28:49.520
Want me to feed you?

00:28:50.760 --> 00:28:51.840
So your hands are free for the guitar.

00:28:53.680 --> 00:28:54.360
It's fine.

00:28:59.360 --> 00:29:01.080
I wanna eat barbeque.

00:29:05.240 --> 00:29:06.000
Then help yourself.

00:29:15.960 --> 00:29:17.280
(What are you laughing at?)

00:29:18.360 --> 00:29:20.440
(Good luck with that, moron.)

00:29:43.320 --> 00:29:43.960
P'Toh.

00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:47.400
Are you drunk?
You should head up to bed.

00:29:49.920 --> 00:29:51.600
I'm not drunk...

00:29:54.680 --> 00:29:58.400
You can barely keep your head up.
I'll take you to your room.

00:29:59.520 --> 00:30:00.400
I'm getting sleepy anyway.

00:30:03.920 --> 00:30:06.520
Don't worry. I'll take him.

00:30:10.760 --> 00:30:12.880
You're still having fun. Just stay here.

00:30:13.960 --> 00:30:14.880
I'll take my...

00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:15.880
Stay right where you are.

00:30:16.800 --> 00:30:19.200
If you go up, I know you'll
ditch me and go to sleep.

00:30:19.960 --> 00:30:21.200
I've got this.

00:30:23.680 --> 00:30:24.360
Come on, P'Toh.

00:30:25.840 --> 00:30:26.640
Let's go.

00:30:46.840 --> 00:30:48.960
Easy does it.

00:30:50.840 --> 00:30:52.720
My head's spinning.

00:30:54.360 --> 00:30:55.560
It's because you're wasted.

00:30:58.160 --> 00:30:59.640
Get some sleep. You'll feel better.

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:02.640
Well…

00:31:03.480 --> 00:31:04.240
I'm going.

00:31:08.640 --> 00:31:09.680
Stay with me.

00:31:11.280 --> 00:31:12.920
I'm scared of ghosts.

00:31:15.400 --> 00:31:17.720
I had no idea you were a scaredy-cat.

00:31:21.280 --> 00:31:23.120
Stay until I fall asleep.

00:32:07.720 --> 00:32:09.560
If you're worried, just check on him yourself.

00:32:12.480 --> 00:32:14.480
I don't want to leave
you here by yourself, P'Fah.

00:32:17.560 --> 00:32:18.800
Just call me “Fah”.

00:32:21.200 --> 00:32:23.440
“Just Fah”.

00:32:24.960 --> 00:32:25.520
Much better.

00:32:30.120 --> 00:32:31.480
I think that you've…

00:32:32.720 --> 00:32:34.000
been avoiding me.

00:32:37.240 --> 00:32:38.400
I haven't.

00:32:58.360 --> 00:32:59.640
Don't you want to kiss me?

00:33:03.680 --> 00:33:04.400
Fah,

00:33:09.720 --> 00:33:11.000
Jimmy likes you.

00:33:14.160 --> 00:33:15.640
But I don't like him.

00:33:17.440 --> 00:33:18.760
And I'm not looking for anything serious.

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:05.040
It's late. We should head to bed.

00:34:13.320 --> 00:34:14.480
Can I sleep in your room tonight?

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:42.360
Teh, don't give me that look.

00:34:43.240 --> 00:34:46.080
P'Toh was scared of ghosts
and asked me to stay with him.

00:34:48.040 --> 00:34:50.360
Why are you two headed back?

00:34:51.240 --> 00:34:51.880
Run out of snacks?

00:34:53.080 --> 00:34:55.640
No, we're heading to bed.

00:34:57.160 --> 00:35:00.280
I'm driving tomorrow.
Can't risk a headache.

00:35:01.320 --> 00:35:01.840
Let's go.

00:35:05.680 --> 00:35:06.760
We're off to bed.

00:35:07.520 --> 00:35:07.960
Goodnight.

00:35:18.040 --> 00:35:18.800
Move it.

00:35:19.960 --> 00:35:20.560
Now.

00:35:36.080 --> 00:35:37.400
Damn!

00:35:38.320 --> 00:35:39.600
Fah said goodnight to me.

00:35:40.640 --> 00:35:41.720
What did you tell him?

00:35:43.600 --> 00:35:45.560
Just that you like him.

00:35:45.880 --> 00:35:46.680
For real?

00:35:50.840 --> 00:35:51.640
What did he say?

00:35:52.440 --> 00:35:53.760
He didn't say anything.

00:35:54.520 --> 00:35:56.360
You've got to be kidding me!

00:35:56.960 --> 00:35:59.240
Tell me. I wanna know.

00:35:59.240 --> 00:36:01.120
Go ask him yourself.

00:36:02.120 --> 00:36:03.600
I'm dead tired.

00:36:13.960 --> 00:36:16.120
And turn down the AC.
It's frickin' hot.

00:36:17.200 --> 00:36:18.480
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:36:30.720 --> 00:36:32.360
It's already at 19.

00:36:33.080 --> 00:36:34.000
Why is it still hot?

00:36:40.680 --> 00:36:45.240
What should we do?
We're going to be baked alive in here.

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:49.680
You better compensate us tomorrow,
or I'm leaving a nasty review.

00:36:51.360 --> 00:36:53.640
Well? Can't they fix it?

00:36:54.200 --> 00:36:56.040
It's past midnight.
The technicians are all gone.

00:36:57.520 --> 00:36:58.480
Now what?

00:37:00.960 --> 00:37:02.520
Sleep naked like me.

00:37:02.680 --> 00:37:03.880
Hell no.

00:37:10.360 --> 00:37:11.560
Or…

00:37:12.760 --> 00:37:13.800
crash in P'Toh's room.

00:37:14.320 --> 00:37:15.680
No, too cramped.

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:18.920
That's what I want.

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:30.000
Grab your blanket!

00:38:03.160 --> 00:38:04.120
Hey,

00:38:05.040 --> 00:38:06.360
I'll sleep next to Fah.

00:38:09.080 --> 00:38:10.640
Whatever.

00:38:12.360 --> 00:38:13.320
I'll crash on the floor.

00:38:14.320 --> 00:38:19.160
Sleep next your crush like a K-drama.

00:38:21.480 --> 00:38:24.880
Make sure your body
stays “stiff”. Nothing else.

00:38:24.880 --> 00:38:25.800
Screw you.

00:38:26.480 --> 00:38:30.240
I'll tell your brother the real you.

00:38:30.960 --> 00:38:32.160
Go to sleep already.

00:38:46.520 --> 00:38:47.440
Teh.

00:38:48.200 --> 00:38:48.920
Now what?

00:38:50.240 --> 00:38:51.720
I can't sleep next to Fah.

00:38:52.520 --> 00:38:53.680
P'Tohs in the way.

00:38:54.440 --> 00:38:55.840
And you're next to him.

00:38:58.120 --> 00:38:59.440
Just sleep here with me.

00:39:00.280 --> 00:39:02.520
Nah, my back will be trashed.

00:39:06.160 --> 00:39:07.000
Teh.

00:39:07.360 --> 00:39:08.160
What now?

00:39:08.920 --> 00:39:10.280
I'll sleep next to your brother.

00:39:10.920 --> 00:39:14.120
Yeah, fine. I'm out.

00:39:14.720 --> 00:39:16.000
And stop bothering me.

00:39:18.520 --> 00:39:19.160
I'm sleeping.

00:40:27.000 --> 00:40:28.320
Can I sleep here with you?

00:40:30.040 --> 00:40:31.200
My blanket got snatched.

00:40:38.960 --> 00:40:40.440
I saw you at the club once.

00:40:41.880 --> 00:40:43.200
But I guess you didn't notice me.

00:40:45.200 --> 00:40:46.000
Really?

00:40:48.200 --> 00:40:50.440
You're so charming.

00:40:52.520 --> 00:40:56.160
No wonder you're always with someone new.

00:40:57.520 --> 00:40:58.960
Can I ask you something?

00:41:01.960 --> 00:41:03.560
Do you ever want something serious?

00:41:08.000 --> 00:41:09.320
I used to,

00:41:11.040 --> 00:41:13.960
but I don't really know what love feels like.

00:41:16.360 --> 00:41:19.880
Every relationship I've had was just a thrill.

00:41:21.680 --> 00:41:24.800
Once the spark is gone, I'm done.

00:41:27.600 --> 00:41:28.320
So…

00:41:29.560 --> 00:41:31.440
just one-night stands then?

00:41:35.360 --> 00:41:36.480
I just feel…

00:41:38.480 --> 00:41:41.040
if I can't love someone with my whole soul,

00:41:44.520 --> 00:41:46.200
it's better to be alone.

00:41:47.840 --> 00:41:51.320
How can it be love without devotion?

00:41:54.320 --> 00:41:56.960
What if…

00:42:00.200 --> 00:42:01.680
you finally find the one…

00:42:03.840 --> 00:42:06.400
you can give all your heart to…

00:42:08.520 --> 00:42:11.360
but they don't feel the same,

00:42:12.920 --> 00:42:14.280
wouldn't that destroy you?

00:42:17.680 --> 00:42:21.200
Well… At least I got to “love” someone.

00:44:02.360 --> 00:44:02.880
Jimmy?

00:44:04.600 --> 00:44:05.240
P'Toh.

00:44:06.640 --> 00:44:07.960
Let me cover your ears.

00:44:24.040 --> 00:44:26.640
Jimmy? Are you okay?

00:44:39.640 --> 00:44:40.600
P'Toh…

00:44:42.200 --> 00:44:43.120
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

00:44:45.720 --> 00:44:46.600
I just…

00:44:48.720 --> 00:44:50.240
need a hug right now.

00:45:57.200 --> 00:45:58.200
Damn…

00:46:00.200 --> 00:46:01.320
You're…

00:46:03.280 --> 00:46:05.200
so tempting like what Teh said.

00:46:32.200 --> 00:46:32.800
No.

00:46:34.920 --> 00:46:35.640
This isn't right.

00:47:04.880 --> 00:47:07.360
At least he respects you, Toh.

00:47:17.320 --> 00:47:19.440
(Next Episode)
There's one rule of mine you should know.

00:47:23.960 --> 00:47:28.120
Do you realize you haven't
been yourself since the trip?

00:47:29.840 --> 00:47:32.040
Did you tell P'Toh that I like Fah?

00:47:32.200 --> 00:47:33.640
- How could you...
- I like Fah.

00:47:34.360 --> 00:47:35.320
Or do you like him too?

00:47:37.600 --> 00:47:40.440
Why don't you trust us?

00:47:41.000 --> 00:47:42.480
I've been his friend for a long time.

00:47:43.400 --> 00:47:44.600
I know exactly what he's capable of.